dataList.appIntro:
This app is an interface of a football bet tips and bet predictions machine. And here, we are serving to you its football betting tips freely. Our bet machine analyses every betting odds and selections and serves to you. As you know football has various statistics such as condition of teams, past matches, team values, pitch conditions and so on (excuse us about secrecy of our algorithm, we can't give you more examples). By analyzing these parameters, it gives the best betting tip for a football match. But we send to our bet machine and it is now analysing hundreds of parameters of each football match and giving you best football betting tips. 
This is not at all. You can see future football games and their free bet tips from 4-5 days before. Also our machine analyses probabilities of full time results, double chances and in near future full time total goals over and under, half time results of a football match. 
Machine analysing football matches with its machine learning algorithms that we wrote and gives you free bet predictions and free bet tips everyday. It serves hundreds free football betting tips in a week. 
This application gives you free daily betting predictions and free bet tips. Machine learning algorithms analyze data and try to give you accurate predictions. 
Also you can track football league stats and past averages of Full Time Results, Half Time Results, Total Goals Ranges.
